Japan’s Third Extra Budget May Total 12 Trillion Yen, Kyodo Says

-- B y   T a k e h i k o   K u m a k u r a
-- 
2011-10-20T02:50:18Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-20/japan-s-third-extra-budget-may-total-12-trillion-yen-kyodo-says.html
Japan ’s third extra budget may total
12 trillion yen ($156 billion), of which 9 trillion yen will be
allocated to post-earthquake reconstruction,  Kyodo News 
reported, without saying where it obtained the information.  The Cabinet will adopt the budget tomorrow.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Takehiko Kumakura at 
